/>\n所以唔該大家係大肆宣傳罷工既必要性 唔係屌醫護"},{"pid":"6f7f362a47ad332853c93d1f4816df1419fcccae","tid":1840771,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53a2ecf8703bd0539b27451b81b1278451229f33","tid":1840771,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89838713dcd6bb12993d5346f41fb4b1f30af09e","tid":1840771,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"232632bb915db516938e55daa5d72aae6d3933cf","tid":1840771,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"你地唔好再屌醫護點解唔敢罷<br />\n人地罷你又幫唔幫手文宣 同佢地一齊罷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"醫護一罷，所有人都會罷。沒有醫護，沒有醫療保障，日日任由病毒輸入，邊個夠膽翻工？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n但有啲連登仔屌佢地奴隸心態<br />\n好老實講 佢地都好怕隔離嗰個睬你都傻<br />\n所以唔該大家係大肆宣傳罷工既必要性 唔係屌醫護"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"建議醫護頂不足壓力可以殺大陸病人減壓。"},{"pid":"bad5b14ee30850358595a207c17fa56ade388da1","tid":1840771,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"佢就係想你病晒 跟住就要靠政府"},{"pid":"f2c818b10a045bb004d3e2823ee2560e4ec68c88","tid":1840771,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e29f1773e055dd815d03ee6acd362091b767112","tid":1840771,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a132dc0d2dda7e7e9b394b668d581620124d8518","tid":1840771,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32575306f0d96ed7d711b013008c1816c0aabde","tid":1840771,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9184a8cffcf85591769db1d2bf60b15dbc863fc6","tid":1840771,"uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"他日光復到香港<br />\n一定要捉林奠入冊判佢意圖謀殺"},{"pid":"a1074aa30b09b32f3c40ede8613672dc3a86e94e","tid":1840771,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得宜家咁緊急關頭 全部飛大陸嘅機師空姐空少都應該要罷工 入境處職員都應該要 香港人快啲自救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd51afe6d64e9dc1fea661fefb2529c2b8c20c5c","tid":1840771,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:28:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35739cd9341408f0068d56f7c148890c76152e0d","tid":1840771,"uid":147299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:29:46.000Z","msg":"都話趁着新沙士 打擊示威熱潮囉！"}]}